	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi postremas tuas 17. iunii, et mirum, quod nullam facias mentionem de meis postremis, quas per mulierculas curavi ad te perferendas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratissimum autem fuit, quod, que tractaturus sis in Decadibus tuis, tam fuse significaveris, neque utiliorem laborem potuisses ecclesiae turbatę conferre, et prudenter etiam facis, quod articulos Interimistarum refellis sine stomacho sicque piis ingentem consolationem offers in iis turbis, cum nemo audeat<note type="margin">a.R.: audiat!</note> publice contra tam superbum et fastuosum librum scribere sine periculo.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod si voles de statu Saxonicarum ecclesiarum certissima scire, hunc tabellarium examinare poteris et mira quędam audies stupendaque.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name" ref="2301">Osiander</persName> taxat nostras ecclesias in suis libellis, quos in <placeName type="auto_name">Prussia</placeName> edidit, quos tamen nondum vidi, sed habebo brevi.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dissident pastores in <placeName type="auto_name" ref="61">Saxonia</placeName> et certant ad sanguinem usque de adiaphoris.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus illorum misereatur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nosti praeterea <persName type="auto_name">Psalterium Musculi</persName> commentariis illustratum sub prelo esse <persName type="auto_name">Oporinico</persName> et <persName type="auto_name">Nazianzeni</persName> opera Gręca et Latina, quę extant, <persName type="auto_name" ref="5213">Hervagius</persName> conatur imprimere <persName type="auto_name" ref="17832">Bernhardi</persName> opera, si sciret exemplaria quędam manuscripta, ut posset quędam conferre.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si tu nosti aliqua, rogo, velis indicare in gratiam studiosorum, neque dubito alibi latere aut <placeName>Sangalli</placeName> aut in Eremo d. Virginis vel alio in quodam loco.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vestros exhibuisse spectaculum egregium de creatione mundi et aliis rebus quis non laudaret cum ob materiam convenientem tum ob industriam, qua vos Tigurini uti soletis prę cęteris.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nihil autem de nostro sentis?</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod cum ingenti magistratus sumptu fuit exhibitum.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">20. iunii 1550.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutato nomine meo d. <persName type="auto_name">Theodorum</persName>, <persName type="auto_name" ref="8127">Pellicanum</persName>, <persName type="auto_name" ref="8011">Gvaltherum</persName> et <persName type="auto_name" ref="1214">Frisium</persName>.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsi nuper de mittendo ceracio<note type="margin">a.R.: seraceo...!</note> sed timeo, ne acceperis literas; si commode poteris, <foreign xml:lang="de">so schicken mir ein guͦten <placeName type="auto_name">Glarner</placeName> krut ziger, und was ir darumb gegen,</foreign> hoc reddam bona fide.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale iterum et aeternum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName type="auto_name">Gastius</persName> ex animo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. Tragutum <placeName type="auto_name">Siciliae</placeName> imminere multis navigiis nosti.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gliscit bellum aut in Hispania aut in Italia.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName type="auto_name" ref="944">Maurus</persName>, <persName type="auto_name" ref="17970">Gallicus</persName> legatus, ad nos heri venit telam orsurus novam.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Paulus Vergerius</persName> <placeName type="auto_name" ref="492">Argentoratum</placeName> petiit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Insigni theologo et pastori vigilantissimo d. Heinrycho Bullingero, praeceptori suo pepetuo laudando.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName type="auto_name" ref="587">Zurich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
